    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated halloumi</strong> and cook for 1-2 min on each side or until crispy and golden brown on both sides – this is your <strong>crispy halloumi</strong></p>",
