    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in the oven for 5 min or until they're hot and crusty, then carefully slice in half before serving</p><p>Combine the<strong> sliced tomato </strong>and <strong>cucumber discs </strong>in a bowl with the <strong>remaining chopped mint</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cucumber & tomato salad</strong></p>",
