    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, top your<strong> crusty ciabatta base </strong>with the <strong>crispy halloumi</strong>, a dollop of <strong>tzatziki</strong>, a handful of <strong>herby fries</strong> and the<strong> crusty ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>halloumi Souvlaki-style sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining herby fries</strong>, <strong>cucumber & tomato salad</strong> and any <strong>remaining tzatziki </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
